name: Cubecalipse
description:
Simple game made for my first gamejam(24 hours). It was created within 16 hours coding session. 

I created music, code and most graphics/models for it. Only few particles comes from free effect package made by Synty Studios and sound from Kenney.nl sound effect package. I was planning to add a minigun to it but unfortunetly I didn't have enough time :/ Hope you enjoy! :)
